de.rwth.i2.attestor.phases.modelChecking.modelChecker

Class Assertion

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.phases.modelChecking.modelChecker.Assertion

  • public class Assertion
extends Object
    This class implements the states of the tableau method proof structure. Each state consists of a program state and a list of (sub)formulae, which together form an assertion, that has to be discharged.
    Author:
    christina

      • addFormula

        public void addFormula(de.rwth.i2.attestor.generated.node.Node formula)
        This method adds a formula to the list of formulae in case it is not already contained (otherwise no action is performed). Note that add respects the insertion order forced by the tableau method, i.e. next formulae are inserted at the back of the list, while all remaining formulae are inserted at its beginning.
        Parameters:
        formula, - the formula to be added
